 if they experience signs and symptoms of hyperkalemia such as nausea, vomiting, weakness, listlessness, tingling of the extremities, paralysis, confusion, weak pulse, and a slow or irregular heartbeat.', 'Synergism', NULL, NULL, 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', 1767317476);
